OL,3,CIsland Commonwealth baton celebrates
OL,4,Ccows, lilies, and a lighthouse
OL,6,FYou couldn't get more Scottish than
OL,7,Fceremonial bagpipes playing to
OL,8,Fofficially reveal Jersey's
OL,9,FCommonwealth baton, celebrating the
OL,10,Fisland's culture.
OL,12,FAhead of the Commonwealth Games next
OL,13,Fmonth in Glasgow, each nation and
OL,14,Fterritory has created its own object,
OL,15,Fwhich is a break in the previous
OL,16,Ftradition that saw a single baton
OL,17,Ftravelling across the world.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
