OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780506355
OL,3,CIsland Commonwealth baton celebrates
OL,4,Ccows, lilies, and a lighthouse
OL,6,FJersey artist Nicholas Romeril
OL,7,Fdesigned, handcrafted, and painted the
OL,8,Fisland's torch, which will feature
OL,9,Falongside the other 73 Commonwealth
OL,10,Fterritories at the opening ceremony.
OL,12,FEach side of the tetrahedron
OL,13,Frepresents what he believes defines
OL,14,Fthe island's identity: Jersey cows,
OL,15,FJersey Lilies, and La Corbiere
OL,16,FLighthouse.
OL,18,FNicholas is thrilled by the
OL,19,Fopportunity to showcase Jersey on a
OL,20,Fglobal platform and is excited about
OL,21,Fall the eyes that could see his work.
OL,26,@wD@\qr
