OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780506355
OL,3,CIsland Commonwealth baton celebrates
OL,4,Ccows, lilies, and a lighthouse
OL,6,F"It makes me very proud; I'm a very,
OL,7,Fvery proud Jerseyman, so whatever I
OL,8,Fcan do to help promote and celebrate
OL,9,FJersey is a great thing.
OL,11,F"All I hope is that it stands out
OL,12,Famong the rest of them."
OL,14,FTeam Jersey will have 21 athletes
OL,15,Fcompeting in the games, which will run
OL,16,Ffrom this summer from 23 July to 2
OL,17,FAugust.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
