OL,3,CIsland Commonwealth baton celebrates
OL,4,Ccows, lilies, and a lighthouse
OL,6,FHannah Sterry is the youngest of those
OL,7,Fathletes. It will be the 17-year-old's
OL,8,Ffirst Commonwealth Games, and she
OL,9,Fhopes to achieve her personal best in
OL,10,Fswimming.
OL,12,FHannah said the pressure and nerves
OL,13,Fhaven't yet kicked in, explaining: "It
OL,14,Fdoesn't happen often, and it's very
OL,15,Frare, so being able to qualify for and
OL,16,Fget selected is just amazing.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
