OL,3,CIsland Commonwealth baton celebrates
OL,4,Ccows, lilies, and a lighthouse
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Malcom De Souza is no
OL,7,Fstranger to competing on a global
OL,8,Fstage. Malcom will be attending his
OL,9,Ffifth games; he made his bowls
OL,10,FCommonwealth debut a decade and a half
OL,11,Fago in Delhi.
OL,13,FHe told ITV News about the pride he
OL,14,Ffeels when wearing the Island's colour
OL,15,Fon the Commonwealth stage, saying:
OL,16,F"After representing my first, I never
OL,17,Fthought that I'd make it five.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
