PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1780506355
OL,3,CIsland Commonwealth baton celebrates
OL,4,Ccows, lilies, and a lighthouse
OL,6,F"It's always an unbelievable moment to
OL,7,Fput on the Jersey shirt on any
OL,8,Foccasion just to represent the
OL,9,Fislands."
OL,11,FThis week, a range of community events
OL,12,Fwill take place across the island to
OL,13,Fgive us a chance to be part of the
OL,14,Fglobal celebrations.
OL,16,FRelay week has been launched with the
OL,17,Funveiling of Jersey's baton the big
OL,18,Freveal at the Government House by
OL,19,FJersey's Lieutenant Governor.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
