OL,3,CIsland Commonwealth baton celebrates
OL,4,Ccows, lilies, and a lighthouse
OL,6,FSo, what would be His Excellency's
OL,7,Fsport of choice if he had to compete
OL,8,Fin the Commonwealth Games? Well, it
OL,9,Fcertainly wouldn't be sprinter, but he
OL,10,Fwouldn't mind joining Malcom's bowls
OL,11,Fteam.
OL,13,FI did of course tell Jersey's
OL,14,FLieutenant Governor we would welcome
OL,15,Fan invitation back to see how he is
OL,16,Fgetting on for his 2030 Commonwealth
OL,17,FGames training with Malcom.
OL,19,FThat is of course, if he decides to
OL,20,Ftake up the challenge.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
